458
00:24:03,692 --> 00:24:08,488
BLOOD CENTER

459
00:24:10,115 --> 00:24:12,242
SAVE LIVES BY DONATING BLOOD

460
00:24:12,325 --> 00:24:14,035
MOVE TICKET FOR EVERY DONOR

461
00:24:22,127 --> 00:24:23,962
