462
00:24:24,838 --> 00:24:26,423
I only accepted them
because we're neighbors.

463
00:24:26,715 --> 00:24:27,799
Sir.

464
00:24:28,049 --> 00:24:29,259
No bones.

465
00:24:29,467 --> 00:24:30,927
I don't want any bones.

