I'm going to eat all alone.

487
00:26:15,949 --> 00:26:18,159
Do you think you won't get caught
if you grill that at home?

488
00:26:19,995 --> 00:26:22,080
That's the difference between you and me.

489
00:26:22,622 --> 00:26:25,667
