803
00:44:43,639 --> 00:44:46,350
Don't worry. I want some fresh air.

804
00:44:48,519 --> 00:44:50,312
Well... Let's go.

805
00:44:54,400 --> 00:44:56,068
We say no to senior care facilities!

806
00:44:56,151 --> 00:44:58,112
We oppose building a nursing home!

807
00:44:58,195 --> 00:45:00,322
-We oppose!
-We oppose!

808
00:45:00,447 --> 00:45:03,492
No construction without
Jagok-dong residents' consent!

809
00:45:03,575 --> 00:45:05,160
Stop immediately!

810
00:45:05,244 --> 00:45:07,371
-Stop!
-Stop!

811
00:45:09,206 --> 00:45:10,874
Ma'am, you can lean on me.

812
00:45:10,958 --> 00:45:12,376
-Hold on to my arm.
