826
00:45:52,082 --> 00:45:54,209
If you're here for a news story,
you can go ahead.

827
00:45:57,129 --> 00:45:59,465
What? This doesn't count

828
00:45:59,798 --> 00:46:02,634
as a field you talked about?

829
00:46:03,177 --> 00:46:05,846
Then again,
for a promising reporter like you,

830
00:46:06,430 --> 00:46:09,558
a field must be where the history changes.

831
00:46:10,851 --> 00:46:13,812
But you know what? For these people,

832
00:46:14,354 --> 00:46:17,065
this is as important as the things
that change the history.

833
00:46:18,275 --> 00:46:19,401
These old ladies?

834
00:46:20,110 --> 00:46:22,905
Yes, the facilities might be
meant for them,

835
00:46:22,988 --> 00:46:26,366
but falling house prices hurt them
more than bad health.

836
00:46:26,742 --> 00:46:29,036
