864
00:48:06,174 --> 00:48:08,343
We say no to senior care facilities!

865
00:48:08,677 --> 00:48:11,013
We oppose building a nursing home!

866
00:48:11,179 --> 00:48:13,348
-We oppose!
-We oppose!

867
00:48:13,765 --> 00:48:16,602
Goodness. Having a young lady with us

868
