but that would humiliate you.

879
00:48:57,100 --> 00:49:00,187
So I decided to stay. What kind
of pervert would think that?

880
00:49:09,446 --> 00:49:12,074
I knew it. I did think he sounded

881
00:49:12,157 --> 00:49:15,327
