a performance or something.

889
00:49:36,890 --> 00:49:38,600
You work here?

890
00:49:38,684 --> 00:49:41,895
I know the manager here,
so I sometimes fill in at night.

891
00:49:47,693 --> 00:49:49,111
I'll pay.

892
00:49:50,112 --> 00:49:52,864
I apologize for lecturing you
about being on the field.

893
00:49:53,699 --> 00:49:55,534
Earlier when you were talking to me,

894
00:49:56,743 --> 00:50:00,163
I thought you sounded logical and neutral.

895
00:50:00,664 --> 00:50:02,833
And just the right amount
of emotional appeal at the climax.

896
00:50:04,126 --> 00:50:05,627
It would have made a stunning news story.

897
00:50:08,130 --> 00:50:09,715
You're still judging, though.

898
00:50:10,173 --> 00:50:11,341
The thing is,

899
00:50:12,342 --> 00:50:14,886
I'm a bit angry

900
00:50:14,970 --> 00:50:16,972
at the TBC news anchor.

901
00:50:17,055 --> 00:50:18,223
You mean Jang Seo-yeon?

902
00:50:19,808 --> 00:50:22,102
She's always been like that.

903
00:50:22,477 --> 00:50:23,895
She was always pretentious...

904
00:50:27,149 --> 00:50:28,316
So how much is it?

905
00:50:30,318 --> 00:50:32,612
It's on me. As an apology.

906
00:50:35,282 --> 00:50:37,951
That's not really necessary.

907
00:50:39,411 --> 00:50:41,079
I'll take this too.

908
00:50:45,041 --> 00:50:46,084
This...

909
00:50:47,294 --> 00:50:48,378
Sorry.

910
00:50:48,920 --> 00:50:50,046
Oh, you're here.

911
00:50:55,969 --> 00:50:58,889
-That's so romantic.
-Lower your voice.

912
00:50:59,306 --> 00:51:03,268
He must have lectured you
because he was interested in you.

913
00:51:03,351 --> 00:51:05,145
That's so romantic. My gosh.

914
00:51:05,228 --> 00:51:08,231
You're going too far.
We only met recently.

915
00:51:08,565 --> 00:51:10,817
It doesn't always take a long time
to fall for someone.

916
00:51:11,818 --> 00:51:12,903
It's not like that.

917
00:51:22,329 --> 00:51:24,581
I've filled the shelves in the back.
I'll get going now.

918
00:51:25,665 --> 00:51:26,750
Have a nice day.

919
00:51:28,293 --> 00:51:29,461
Had a nice day.

920
00:51:33,381 --> 00:51:35,175
