925
00:51:51,358 --> 00:51:54,236
The sikhye is ready. You like it, right?

926
00:51:54,319 --> 00:51:57,781
-I'll get going.
-Okay. Bye.

927
00:51:58,657 --> 00:52:00,909
The girl earlier...

928
00:52:01,326 --> 00:52:04,830
I mean the girl with big eyes
like those of a cow's.

929
00:52:04,913 --> 00:52:06,289
Oh, what about her?

930
00:52:06,665 --> 00:52:09,709
She is the daughter of the hair salon
down the street.

931
00:52:09,793 --> 00:52:12,045
Apparently, she is getting married soon.

932
00:52:13,505 --> 00:52:14,673
I see.

933
00:52:15,173 --> 00:52:18,385
I was hoping you'd go out with her.

934
00:52:18,802 --> 00:52:20,679
What a disappointment.

935
00:52:21,346 --> 00:52:23,223
Why would you say that? Let's go in.

936
00:52:23,306 --> 00:52:25,976
-Go in. Hurry up.
-All right.

937
00:52:26,309 --> 00:52:28,770
There's no telling what will happen
between a guy and a girl.

938
00:52:28,979 --> 00:52:30,480
Sang-eun is right in that.

939
00:52:30,939 --> 00:52:33,859
