when they grow old and sick.

964
00:53:37,797 --> 00:53:39,007
Okay, ma'am.

965
00:53:39,633 --> 00:53:40,759
Goodbye.

966
00:53:52,562 --> 00:53:53,605
Up there.

967
00:53:53,813 --> 00:53:57,192
Is there a broadcasting station
at a place like this too?

968
00:53:57,359 --> 00:53:58,485
Broadcasting station?

969
00:54:11,414 --> 00:54:12,624
