Naturally.

1001
00:55:55,810 --> 00:55:57,645
Naturally?

1002
00:55:57,729 --> 00:56:00,732
I'm sorry. It could be tough for her
since she doesn't have

1003
00:56:00,815 --> 00:56:02,317
-much experience.
-What do you mean?

1004
00:56:03,610 --> 00:56:05,653
I used to be so trashy!

1005
00:56:05,862 --> 00:56:07,322
